### 1. Staggered Character Reveal (Each Letter Slides Up Individually)

Visual: Each character of "Attirer Grandeur" starts below its baseline (invisible, clipped by overflow) and slides upward into place one at a time, left to right, with slight easing. The effect looks like the letters are being "dealt" into position. A 0.03-0.05s stagger between characters creates a wave-like cascade.

Technology: Framer Motion (already in your `package.json`) -- no additional dependencies needed.

